      ],
      "text": "Meanwhile, Zaheer explained to Korra that he was going to end the Avatar Cycle and ordered a Red Lotus sentry to give Korra the poison. Once in her body, she entered the Avatar State, though managed to escape before Ming-Hua and Ghazan could kill her. Zaheer escaped through flight but Korra chased after him. Mako and Bolin appeared in time to prevent Ming-Hua and Ghazan from following the two, ultimately defeating the Red Lotus members. However, Ghazan, refusing to go back to prison, brought down the structure by lavabending."
